title: Cambodian defense minister to attend regional security forum in Beijing (Beijing Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Beijing Municipal Government ) Cambodian Deputy Prime Minister and Defense Minister Gen. Tea Banh will attend the sixth Xiangshan Forum in Beijing, China , from Oct. 15 to 18, the defense ministry said in a statement on Tuesday.
